						<summary>

						<p>Slab built into the side wall of the <hi rend="italic">Kōnēru.</hi></p>						

						<p>This is dated <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1655, Paridhāvi, Āśvija śu. 2. Bhānuvāra,</hi> corresponding to <hi rend="bold">1732 A.D., September 10, Sunday 30.</hi></p>						

						<p>Records the construction of the eastern gate in the fort wall of Peddapasapula by Yusupu Khān (Yusuf khān) son of Hajarāti Nawab, Jamshed Khān.</p>						

						</summary>
